proaches (combining RNA-seq, miRNA profiling, and EMSAs) are utilized.\n\n### Source Documentation:\nUnfortunately, due to a technical error, specific PubMed citations were not retrieved in this session. However, existing literature in the field broadly supports the interaction between miRNAs, transcription factors, cytokine signaling, and their expression modulation through epigenetic changes.\n",
